e UK faces remains both serious and</span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt"> </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">sustained and that the nature of that threat is evolving and diversifying</span><span style="color:#464744; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="color:#464744; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">3</span><span style="color:#464744; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">. </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">The UK</span><span style="color:#464744; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">'</span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">s record on CT remains a strong one</span><span style="color:#464744; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">. </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">We continue </span><span style="color:#252523; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">successfully </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">to</span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt"> </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">disrupt attempted </span><span style="color:#252523; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">attacks </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">against this country and its interests overseas. We are</span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt"> </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">becoming more successful at prosecuting and convicting individuals </span><span style="color:#252523; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">engaging </span><span style="color:#131412; font-family:Arial; font-size:11.5pt">in</span><span style="color:#131412; font-famil